{"tid":1568811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「真緊急」其實獨立調查委員會要點搞？","createTime":"2019-09-14T11:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T04:58:27.000Z","uid":51525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b5296d38794cc5d2898f658c571c178edec96a","tid":1568811,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n當中四項真係yes/no question咁簡單<br />\n但係其中<span style=\"color: red;\">成立獨立調查委員會</span><br />\n係無諗過點搞 點先叫收貨<br />\n而家唔得出共識/接受原則<br />\n到時實行會大亂<br />\n我想提出幾個大方針俾大家傾下先<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.有人話過類似當年查警察收規咁搞<br />\n咁實際情況同細節到底要點做？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.個委員會有幾大權力先夠？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.成立委員會嘅目的係咩？（查濫權濫暴行為/改革警隊/再重新檢討警隊守則？）</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4.當委員會調查完成之後要點做？（長期成立 取代監警會/只會係暫時性成立？）</span></span>"},{"pid":"73e20569f53b2f9996e797665330f18b1363a584","tid":1568811,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:46:58.000Z","msg":"先唔講人選<br />\n淨係個大綱其實都未定<br />\n講就好好聽 但係實際點做<br />\n大家直情係無概念<br />\n連成立嘅重點同目的係咩都未知"},{"pid":"81f0cc07cf9b316f8d6c6ff4f05a0f74e6126457","tid":1568811,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b5283572cd6774564215910e17c3152326c8204","tid":1568811,"uid":124146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"成立左就得 咩都唔洗做"},{"pid":"8735995a1a0bf24fdeb18018a4f6ee14b4ed6220","tid":1568811,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAABnFb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAABnFb.png&h=5bd749e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/caLar6x.png\" da